{"parse":{"title":"Apology Project","pageid":2007980,"revid":857597407,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>The Apology Project</b>, a 1980 conceptual art project, was created by <a href=\"/wiki/Allan_Bridge\" title=\"Allan Bridge\">Allan Bridge</a> who employed the pseudonym Mr. Apology. Bridge used an <a href=\"/wiki/Answering_machine\" title=\"Answering machine\">answering machine</a> to record confessions from anonymous callers. More than 1000 hours of confession were recorded, ranging from common confessions to ritualistic murders.\n</p><p>Some of the confessions were published in Bridge's magazine <i>Apology</i>.\n</p><p>This Apology Project is not to be confused with the Apology Project of Elliniko Teatro, a theatrical production based on Plato's The Apology of Socrates, featuring Yannis Simonides (see <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://www.ellinikotheatro.org\">http://www.ellinikotheatro.org</a>.)\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Apology_Project&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Grouphug.us&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Grouphug.us (page does not exist)\">grouphug.us</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Grouphelp.org&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Grouphelp.org (page does not exist)\">grouphelp.org</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Apology_Project&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.apologyproject.com/\">The Apology Project</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://grouphelp.org/\">Group Help</a></li></ul>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<table class=\"metadata plainlinks stub\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"background:transparent\"><tbody><tr><td><a href=\"/wiki/File:La_danse_(I)_by_Matisse.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Stub icon\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/2/2e/La_danse_%28I%29_by_Matisse.jpg/40px-La_danse_%28I%29_by_Matisse.jpg\" width=\"40\" height=\"27\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/2/2e/La_danse_%28I%29_by_Matisse.jpg/60px-La_danse_%28I%29_by_Matisse.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/2/2e/La_danse_%28I%29_by_Matisse.jpg/80px-La_danse_%28I%29_by_Matisse.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"1988\" data-file-height=\"1318\" /></a></td><td><i>This <a href=\"/wiki/Modern_art\" title=\"Modern art\">modern art</a>-related article is a <a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:Stub\" title=\"Wikipedia:Stub\">stub</a>. You can help Wikipedia by <a class=\"external text\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Apology_Project&amp;action=edit\">expanding it</a>.</i><div class=\"plainlinks hlist navbar mini\" style=\"position: absolute; right: 15px; display: none;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/wiki/Template:Modern-art-stub\" title=\"Template:Modern-art-stub\"><abbr title=\"View this template\">v</abbr></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/wiki/Template_talk:Modern-art-stub\" title=\"Template talk:Modern-art-stub\"><abbr title=\"Discuss this template\">t</abbr></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Modern-art-stub&amp;action=edit\"><abbr title=\"Edit this template\">e</abbr></a></li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"metadata plainlinks stub\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"background:transparent\"><tbody><tr><td><a href=\"/wiki/File:Nuvola_apps_package_graphics.svg\" cla